	<title>Materials</title>
    
	<subsection>
		<title>Textbooks</title>
		<p>
            Our primary textbook will be <url href="https://openstax.org/details/books/algebra-and-trigonometry-2e">Openstax Algebra and Trigonometry 2e</url>. 
            This is a free textbook you can access online. You may purchase a paper copy for a small price, if you want.
		</p>
	</subsection>

	<subsection>
		<title>Supplies</title>
		<p>
            In this class, you will need:
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <p>
                        Pencils with erasers
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>
                        Note paper of your choice
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>
                        <url href="https://bookstore.pcc.edu/store4/MerchDetail?MerchID=1621016">Engineering paper</url> for completing your homework write-ups
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>
                        Ruler, straightedge, or protractor for drawing neat graphs. The bookstore has a bunch of nice options.
                    </p>
                </li>
            </ul>
		</p>
	</subsection>

	<subsection>
        <title>Software/Hardware/Equipment</title>
		<p>
