            browser installed. We will be accessing the following:
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <p>
                        <url href="https://online.pcc.edu/">D2L Brightspace</url>, our primary learning platform with PCC,
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>
                        <url href="https://www.desmos.com/">Desmos</url>, a free online graphing calculator,
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>
                        <url href="https://www.myopenmath.com/">MyOpenMath</url>, where you will complete weekly homework assignments and quizzes, and
                    </p>
